        "description": {
          "value": "<p>You telepathically rack the target’s mind and body with agonizing pain that imposes a –2 penalty to ability checks, attack rolls, and skill checks. A target that succeeds at a Will saving throw reduces the duration to 1 round.</p>",
          "chat": "",
          "unidentified": ""
        },
        "source": "",
